Class TuitionManagerController

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.TuitionManagerController
public class TuitionManagerController extends Object
A class that handles input and output for the entire Tuition Manager GUI. Takes in input through TextFields and Button groups to display the appropriate data on the output panel.
Author:
Sharukh Khan, Hamad Naveed
